@startuml componentes_ecosistema
' Arquitectura del ecosistema: 2 backends + 2 frontends + BD compartida
title Ecosistema Financiera Qapaq — Componentes

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor "Personal\n(asesor/comité)" as Per
actor "Cliente" as Cli

package "Frontend" {
  [Front Core\nReact :5173] as FC
  [Front HB\nReact :5174] as FH
}

package "Backend (FastAPI)" {
  [Core API :8001] as BC
  [Homebanking API :8002] as BH
}

database "PostgreSQL\nbd_core_financiero" as DB

Per --> FC
Cli --> FH
FC --> BC : REST + JWT (personal)
FH --> BH : REST + JWT (cliente)
BC --> DB
BH --> DB

note bottom of DB
  80 tablas. Datos recalibrados (SGN):
  2 productos (Empresarial/Consumo),
  mora ~13%. Ambos backends escriben
  en las MISMAS tablas (integración real).
end note

note right of BC
  Scoring, solicitud, comité,
  desembolso, dashboard, bandeja,
  productos dinámicos, recuperaciones
end note

note right of BH
  Login cliente, cuentas,
  movimientos, pagar, solicitar
end note
@enduml
